comments: White (CHI) moves alongside Nembhard's (IND) path and absorbs the contact initiated by Nembhard during the drive toward the rim.
Caruso (CHI) reaches in and initiates contact with Nesmith's (IND) body that affects his SQBR.
Turner (IND) initiates contact with White's (CHI) arm, which affects his ability to move into his upward shooting motion during the driving shot attempt.
Turner (IND) firms up in Dosunmu's (CHI) path and both players engage in marginal contact as the screen is set.
Caruso (CHI) briefly grasps Turner's (IND) arm as both players position themselves for the loose ball.
Nesmith (IND) does not establish himself in LaVine's (CHI) path and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) firms up in Caruso's (CHI) path and both players engage in marginal contact as the screen is set.
White (CHI) moves alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the driving shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and legally pivots off of it before his jump shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul against Turner (IND).
Caruso (CHI) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
Vucevic (CHI) slightly extends his arm into Nesmith (IND) as the pick is being set.
Nembhard (IND) commits a take foul against LaVine (CHI).
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul against Hield (IND).
Vucevic (CHI) slightly extends his arms into Nembhard's (IND) path and some contact occurs as the pick is being set.
